title: UFYB 32: Ask Better Questions
itunes:title: Ask Better Questions
description:
This week, I want to teach you one of the best tools that I learned from my coach – the power of asking better questions. Join me as I explain how asking dead-end questions is affecting your brain and show you how to ask questions that stimulate your brain to find answers that will move you toward goals.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/32

Learn about the UnF*ck Your Brain program and sign up for the next round at  https://unfckyourbrain.com/program.
